<taxonomicName id="C5A2C87433C5CE0293646B57B322E6A1" authority="Kriebel, 2016" authorityName="Gleason" authorityYear="1945" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Conostegia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Conostegia rubiginosa" order="Myrtales" pageId="139" pageNumber="140" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubiginosa">Conostegia rubiginosa</taxonomicName>
Gleason, Bull. Torrey Bot. Club 72: 473. 1945. Type: Colombia. El Valle: Quebrada de Guapecito, rio Cajambre, Costa del Pacifico, 0-5 m, 16 May 1944, J. Cuatrecasas 17700 (holotype: NY!, isotypes: F!, US!).
</paragraph>
